Summary of Instructions for creating your search service

1. Create a resouce group
2. Create a storage account that will act as the datasource (the data that will be queried for your search by users) in the resource group.
3. Create your search service in the same storage account.
4. Copy details such as the name of storage account, search service, keys etc
5. Upload sample data to the new blob storage using microsoft storage explorer or any other available means.
6.
